{"tid":1600744,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日popo劇本","createTime":"2019-09-28T17:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T17:34:28.000Z","uid":326997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"495b291cef1dcef4de496648b44022994dcbaa5e","tid":1600744,"uid":326997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"最近每次出黎都係跟住黎黎去去兩個劇本走<br />\n唔理有冇不反都好，都係：<br />\n<br />\n劇本1:<br />\n見到一班popo成班人忍唔住屌鳩佢地 <br />\n唱哂歌 起哂綱<br />\npopo派人增援<br />\n突然沖前<br />\nSet rb  對峙<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">清場 大逃亡</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n劇本2:<br />\nPopo四圍撩人<br />\n屌popo<br />\n沖前<br />\nSet rb 對峙<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>清場 大逃亡</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日要show俾國際睇嘅係香港嘅反極權決心同人數，唔係睇勇武點升級點用魔法拖住啲popo<br />\n<br />\n所以希望所有前線都忍下口同手，唔好見佢地行前小小就拆野set rb,同埋聚哂係到d9班popo,<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好咁易俾popo利用到你地嘅憤怒</span>,操控哂啲劇本點行點行，我地要好似以前咁行啲政府對付唔到我地嘅方法，跳出呢個一直鬼打牆嘅局面<br />\n<br />\n因為我地要贏嘅係呢個政府！<br />\n唔係嘴炮班popo發洩憤怒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">絕勇棄武 民利百倍</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a3f550452207a81aa5df69943a7a8f02a3c6a201","tid":1600744,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"卧底演員講得聽既咩？"},{"pid":"16b51904c399c9cc399d05b9ff6a6303a6948257","tid":1600744,"uid":326997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"因為岩岩講嘅係好ideal嘅情況 popo要清場點都清到 但希望嘅係可以減低黎自我地呢邊所造成嘅影響力 唔好俾佢地出師有名 雖然你會話佢地都唔care呢啲"},{"pid":"00b7b39378a7f7812d5642b7d7ffb54f2690e42b","tid":1600744,"uid":326997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jxepeNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjxepeNJ.jpg&h=3cb3ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsgySzq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsgySzq.